  <h2>íƒ€ì›Œ ë””íœìŠ¤ v7.7 (ëª¨ë°”ì¼ ìµœì í™”)</h2>
  <canvas id="gameCanvas" width="480" height="640"></canvas>
  <div id="ui">
    <button id="startBtn" class="btn">â–¶ ì‹œì‘</button>
    <button id="pauseBtn" class="btn">â¸ ë©ˆì¶¤</button>
    <button id="resetBtn" class="btn">ğŸ”„ ë¦¬ì…‹</button>
    <p id="info">ë¼ì´í”„ â¤ï¸: 20 | ëˆ ğŸ’°: 100 | ì›¨ì´ë¸Œ ğŸŒŠ: 1</p>
  </div>
  <div id="towerBar">
    <div class="towerIcon" data-type="basic">ê¸°ë³¸</div>
    <div class="towerIcon" data-type="range">ë²”ìœ„</div>
    <div class="towerIcon" data-type="slow">ìŠ¬ë¡œìš°</div>
    <div class="towerIcon" data-type="multi">ì—°ë°œ</div>
    <div class="towerIcon" data-type="explosive">í­ë°œ</div>
    <div class="towerIcon" data-type="money">ëˆ</div>
    <div class="towerIcon" data-type="flame">í™”ì—¼</div>
